title: BRIEF-JQW appoints Francis Chan Hein Huey as CFO
text:
BRIEF-JQW appoints Francis Chan Hein Huey as CFO Sept 9 
Sept 9 Jqw Plc 
* Appoints Francis Chan Hein Huey to board of company as chief financial officer 
* Kooi Wei Boon has been helping Huey integrate into his new role to ensure that transition process runs smoothly. Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: Trending On Reuters
